verses.text:
This land we took in possession at that time: from Aroer, which is by
the valley of the Arnon, and half the hill country of Gilead with its cities, I gave to the Reubenites
and to the Gadites;

To the Reubenites and to the Gadites I gave from Gilead even to the
valley of the Arnon, the middle of the valley, and its border, even to the river Jabbok, which is the
border of the children of Ammon;
